<title>USA: Ben &amp; Jerry's to repurchase shares.</title>
<headline>Ben &amp; Jerry's to repurchase shares.</headline>
<dateline>BOSTON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ben &amp; Jerry's Homemade Inc said Thursday its board of directors has approved the repurchase of up to 200,000 of its class A common shares.</p>
<p>The company will use the reacquired shares primarily to satisfy future requirements for its stock options under its equity incentive plan and also for other corporate purposes.</p>
<p>The company currently has about 7.3 million class A and class B common shares outstanding. Smith Barney is agent for this program.</p>
<p>((Boston bureau (617) 367-4106))</p>
